div.p: We collected two datasets from two grids. Grid 2(~16000 movies) (PANX1-DM), Grid4(~8000 movies) (PANX3) We obtained a structure at 3.20 Å resolution from grid 2 whereas from grid4, we could obtain a structure at a nominal resolution of 4.32Å. Attached below are the cryoEM map with their respective FSC curve. The manuscript is being revised using the data obtained for PANX1-DM. The data collected at ESRF in this session helped in improving the data quality of one of our structures as required by the reviewers.
